---
title: English-Style Turkey Stew with Roasted Potatoes
description: Grab a woolly sweater and throw a log on the fire. It's time to get cozy with a classic turkey and potato countryside stew. Tonight's version is studded with green peas and we've even added mushrooms to make it extra hearty!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-de-dinde-a-langlaise-62ba3959.jpg
